Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}所有舰只将进行1光年的空间跳跃.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tracer 各机,立即返回.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会跟阿升相差一年时间!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在赶快发邮件...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tracer 二号,请立即返回.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不将这家伙击落...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会来不及的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须返回舰上!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.24,Note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(600,130)}2048年1月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.24,Note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,235)}正在接收信息.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.24,Note1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,315)}正在检查邮箱...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在接收信息......无信息
